dc_description_s: This line data layer represents hydrography for Oneida County, Wisconsin in 2011. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Oneida_HydroLine_2011.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation and the latest version of this data, please visit: http://oneida.ncwrpc.info/
